item.title: For hd severs whats the ip?
item.dc:creator: @Projext Projext
item.description:
@Projext wrote:

You have to enter the IP address of the server you are connecting to. For example “BlahScape.No-Ip.Org”. If you are running the server, use the loopback adapter(127.0.0.1) to connect to your computer.
